						//section
						//	h4 Datasets
						//	p Datasets view shows the  list of the RDF datasets sorted by date last updated by default. Each database icon is linked to the corresponding detailed view. User can sort the datasets by alphabetical order, the number of triples or data provider in ascending or descending order by using the control panel in the bottom of the view. User can also filter the datasets by selecting the database categories.
